{"tid":2297327,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登失態喝斥CBS曾追問其子醜聞的記者｢怎麼就你經常大叫提問?｣ 未答問題即驅離對方","createTime":"2020-11-23T07:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T09:07:20.000Z","uid":204533,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"695addc2ebb11bd5fac8c11f90b46ae653907418","tid":2297327,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國總統當選人拜登上周五（11/21）與民主黨國會領袖會面，討論之後的立法議程安排；雖允許記者採訪，但未安排時間讓記者提問。會議結束之際，哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）記者艾利克森（Bo Erickson）大聲提問疫情下應否復課的問題，遭拜登喝斥：「怎麼就你經常大喊提問 ？」這名記者未得到拜登的回答，就被帶離現場。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">《每日郵報》報導，艾利克森過去與拜登已有「火花」，曾多次向拜登追問有關其子杭特（Hunter Biden）的醜聞。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n拜登周五與副手賀錦麗（Kamala Harris）在德拉瓦州威明頓（Wilmington）巿與眾議院議長裴洛西（Nancy Pelosi）和參院少數黨領袖舒默（Chuck Schumer）會面。<br />\n<br />\n會面結束之際，工作人員要求在場記者離開，這時艾利克森大聲向拜登提問：「拜登先生，武漢肺炎工作小組說已可安全讓學生回去上課，你會鼓勵（教師）工會加強合作，讓孩子回到教室嗎？」拜登沒有回應，反斥責：「怎麼就你經常大喊提問 ？」<br />\n<br />\n艾利克森隨後在推特上傳拜登對他喝斥的影片，不少同業都轉發表示支持。《華盛頓觀察周刊》記者鄧利維（Jerry Dunleavy）寫道：「這是一個好問題，值得拜登作出回應」。<br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司（ABC）記者史特金（Will Steakin）指：「艾利克森做得好，（拜登說他）『大喊』問題也太好笑」。《國會山莊報》記者康查（Joe Concha）嘲諷：「大喊問題未來將被視為不尊重、不良的行為」。<br />\n<br />\n獨立記者吉拉尼（Zaid Jilani）更表示，艾利克森是「想做新聞」，「其他跑拜登線的記者大多只是速記員」。<br />\n<br />\n艾利克森同事、CBS白宮記者芮德（Paula Reid）也寫道：「拜登問了好問題，為甚麼艾利克森是其中唯一提問的人？停課、疫苗、振興方案&mdash;&mdash;有很多重要問題應該問裴洛西和拜登」。<br />\n<br />\n拜登與艾利克森並非首次「交手」，<strong><span class=\"red\">上月艾利克森曾要求拜登回應涉及次子杭特的醜聞時，拜登顯得不滿，「我就知道你會問，我沒有回應，這又是一種抹黑行為，切合你的口味，這是你總會問的問題」。</span></strong>艾利克森是少數曾就此事詢問拜登的主流媒體記者。 （國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201122/5BHGKGVJPZFYVMPCIFKOK4MH4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201122%2F5BHGKGVJPZFYVMPCIFKOK4MH4Q%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnQz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=49f2f2c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201122%2F5BHGKGVJPZFYVMPCIFKOK4MH4Q%2F&h=7927833c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201122/5BHGKGVJPZFYVMPCIFKOK4MH4Q/</a>"},{"pid":"97a2dfa2f985a69c2f7a4662f5a119d28cc16eb6","tid":2297327,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:59:24.000Z","msg":"APPLE段新聞唔客觀, 係自稱當選既拜登, 暫時仲未係當選人囉"},{"pid":"b88f63c6a8b6b86b65e02114a68df8cb8b3cc177","tid":2297327,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/E6rhXL1IS01oIPUq8XkupvwTp0-qvFcLqRPAWNSN7tSV26P3oDo3AS7A8MvqK8iqJsP1D0Mkdi9d5hJiJgkFWQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FE6rhXL1IS01oIPUq8XkupvwTp0-qvFcLqRPAWNSN7tSV26P3oDo3AS7A8MvqK8iqJsP1D0Mkdi9d5hJiJgkFWQ&h=8ac5c251&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8de8859f437c89a05998cf777d79f94fd87a8b32","tid":2297327,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:00:48.000Z","msg":"支持拜登班友有咩好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb90ec17122524875f769fa71630655fe044609c","tid":2297327,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:05:07.000Z","msg":"美國都要無晒攬炒派同埋黑記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3609a5c5d0ae51f82e696cbcbc0484a01f67a41d","tid":2297327,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:23:35.000Z","msg":"獨裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歧視"},{"pid":"4e6dc5581ba95c15cf57d60bb9d10726b6f1e549","tid":2297327,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike"